---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Compliance & Risk — SFC Framework Guide">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-12">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Compliance & Risk</span><span class="lang-zh">合規與風險</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">SFC Framework Guide<br/>for Virtual Assets</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">虛擬資產<br/>SFC框架指南</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl">
      <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong has built the most comprehensive virtual asset regulatory framework in Asia. 12 licensed VATPs, staking approval, stablecoin ordinance, and upcoming legislation for dealers, custodians, and advisors. Here's the complete picture for compliance teams.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">香港已建立亞洲最全面的虛擬資產監管框架。12間持牌VATP、質押批准、穩定幣條例，以及即將推出的交易商、託管人和顧問立法。以下是合規團隊的完整概覽。</span>
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Regulatory Stack -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">The Regulatory Stack</span><span class="lang-zh">監管框架體系</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 text-xs font-medium mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Live</span><span class="lang-zh">已生效</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-white font-bold">VATP</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">12 licensed platforms</span><span class="lang-zh">12間持牌平台</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 text-xs font-medium mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Live</span><span class="lang-zh">已生效</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-white font-bold">Stablecoin</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Ordinance May 2025</span><span class="lang-zh">條例2025年5月</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 text-xs font-medium mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Live</span><span class="lang-zh">已生效</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-white font-bold">Staking</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">SFC approved Apr 2025</span><span class="lang-zh">SFC批准2025年4月</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-yellow-400 text-xs font-medium mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Pending 2026</span><span class="lang-zh">2026年待定</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-white font-bold">
          <span class="lang-en">Dealers+</span><span class="lang-zh">交易商+</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">4 new categories</span><span class="lang-zh">4個新類別</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VATP Deep Dive -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">VATP Licensing — Detailed Requirements</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">VATP牌照 — 詳細要求</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Licensed Platforms (as of Feb 2026)</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">持牌平台（截至2026年2月）</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">HashKey Exchange</span> — <span class="lang-en">Retail + PI, first mover</span><span class="lang-zh">零售 + 專業投資者，先驅</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">OSL Digital Securities</span> — <span class="lang-en">Retail + PI, institutional focus</span><span class="lang-zh">零售 + 專業投資者，機構為主</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">HKVAX</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">HKbitEX</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Accumulus</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">DFX Labs</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Bullish</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Cloud Account</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Crypto.com</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only (pending retail)</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者（待批零售）</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Ex.io</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Matrixport HK</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Thunder Terminal</span> — <span class="lang-en">PI only</span><span class="lang-zh">僅專業投資者</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">
            <span class="lang-en">AML/KYC Requirements</span><span class="lang-zh">反洗錢/KYC要求</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <p><span class="lang-en">Full CDD (Customer Due Diligence) on all clients. Enhanced due diligence for PEPs and high-risk clients.</span><span class="lang-zh">對所有客戶進行完整CDD（客戶盡職調查）。對PEP及高風險客戶進行加強盡職調查。</span></p>
            <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Travel Rule:</span> Compliant with FATF Travel Rule — originator and beneficiary information must accompany virtual asset transfers above HK$8,000.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">旅行規則：</span>符合FATF旅行規則 — 超過HK$8,000的虛擬資產轉移必須附帶匯款人和收款人信息。</span></p>
            <p><span class="lang-en">Suspicious transaction reporting to JFIU (Joint Financial Intelligence Unit).</span><span class="lang-zh">向JFIU（聯合財富情報組）報告可疑交易。</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">
            <span class="lang-en">Custody & Insurance</span><span class="lang-zh">託管與保險</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Cold storage:</span> 98%+ of client assets must be held in cold wallets.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">冷存儲：</span>98%+客戶資產必須存放在冷錢包中。</span></p>
            <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Insurance:</span> Must maintain insurance coverage for virtual assets held in custody.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">保險：</span>必須為託管的虛擬資產維持保險覆蓋。</span></p>
            <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Segregation:</span> Client assets must be segregated from platform proprietary assets.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">隔離：</span>客戶資產必須與平台自有資產分隔。</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stablecoin Ordinance -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Stablecoin Ordinance (May 2025)</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">穩定幣條例（2025年5月）</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Scope:</span><span class="lang-zh">範圍：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Regulates issuance and operation of fiat-referenced stablecoins in HK or marketed to HK persons.</span><span class="lang-zh">規管在香港發行或向香港人士推銷的法幣掛鈎穩定幣的發行和運營。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Reserve:</span><span class="lang-zh">儲備：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">1:1 reserve requirement with high-quality liquid assets. Reserve composition must be disclosed.</span><span class="lang-zh">1:1儲備要求，需高質量流動資產。儲備構成必須披露。</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Applicants:</span><span class="lang-zh">申請人：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">HSBC, Standard Chartered, and OSL are among applicants for stablecoin issuer licenses.</span><span class="lang-zh">HSBC、渣打及OSL為穩定幣發行牌照申請人之一。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Impact:</span><span class="lang-zh">影響：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">If G-SIB banks issue HKD stablecoins, it would be globally significant — dramatically reducing institutional adoption barriers.</span><span class="lang-zh">若G-SIB銀行發行HKD穩定幣，將具全球意義 — 大幅降低機構採用門檻。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Staking Guidelines -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">SFC Staking Guidelines (April 2025)</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">SFC質押指引（2025年4月）</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <div>
          <p class="text-white font-medium mb-2">
            <span class="lang-en">Full custody control</span><span class="lang-zh">完整託管控制</span>
          </p>
          <p><span class="lang-en">Platform must retain full control over staked assets. Cannot delegate to third-party validators without maintaining operational control.</span><span class="lang-zh">平台必須保留對質押資產的完整控制。不可在未維持運營控制的情況下委託第三方驗證者。</span></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white font-medium mb-2">
            <span class="lang-en">Risk disclosure</span><span class="lang-zh">風險披露</span>
          </p>
          <p><span class="lang-en">Clear disclosure of staking risks including slashing, lockup periods, and validator selection criteria to clients.</span><span class="lang-zh">向客戶清楚披露質押風險，包括罰沒、鎖定期及驗證者選擇標準。</span></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white font-medium mb-2">
            <span class="lang-en">Eligible assets</span><span class="lang-zh">合資格資產</span>
          </p>
          <p><span class="lang-en">Currently ETH is the primary staking asset available through licensed VATPs. Additional assets may be approved over time.</span><span class="lang-zh">目前ETH是通過持牌VATP提供的主要質押資產。更多資產可能逐步獲批。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Upcoming 2026 Legislation -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Upcoming 2026 Legislation</span><span class="lang-zh">2026年即將推出的立法</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">The government is preparing legislation for four new categories of virtual asset service providers:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">政府正在為四個新類別的虛擬資產服務提供商準備立法：</span>
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">
            <span class="lang-en">VA Dealers</span><span class="lang-zh">虛擬資產交易商</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <span class="lang-en">Licensing framework for OTC (over-the-counter) virtual asset dealing. Will regulate firms that buy/sell VA as principal or agent outside of licensed VATPs.</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">場外虛擬資產交易的牌照框架。將規管在持牌VATP以外以本人或代理人身份買賣虛擬資產的公司。</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">
            <span class="lang-en">VA Custodians</span><span class="lang-zh">虛擬資產託管人</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <span class="lang-en">Regulation for dedicated custody service providers. Critical for institutional adoption — banks and funds need regulated third-party custody.</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">專門託管服務提供商的監管。對機構採用至關重要 — 銀行和基金需要受監管的第三方託管。</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">
            <span class="lang-en">OTC Brokers</span><span class="lang-zh">場外經紀</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <span class="lang-en">Licensing for crypto brokerage services. Will bring OTC crypto markets under regulatory oversight.</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">加密經紀服務的牌照。將使場外加密市場納入監管。</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">
            <span class="lang-en">VA Advisors</span><span class="lang-zh">虛擬資產顧問</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <span class="lang-en">Regulation of virtual asset investment advisory. Similar to existing SFC Type 4 (advising on securities) license framework.</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">虛擬資產投資顧問的監管。類似現有SFC第4類（就證券提供意見）牌照框架。</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Risk Framework -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Risk Assessment Framework for DeFi Products</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">DeFi產品風險評估框架</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
            <th class="text-left p-4 text-zinc-500 font-medium">
              <span class="lang-en">Product</span><span class="lang-zh">產品</span>
            </th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 text-zinc-500 font-medium">
              <span class="lang-en">SFC Status</span><span class="lang-zh">SFC狀態</span>
            </th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 text-zinc-500 font-medium">
              <span class="lang-en">Key Risks</span><span class="lang-zh">主要風險</span>
            </th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/30">
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium">
              <span class="lang-en">Licensed VATP (BTC/ETH)</span><span class="lang-zh">持牌VATP（BTC/ETH）</span>
            </td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="text-green-400"><span class="lang-en">Regulated</span><span class="lang-zh">受監管</span></span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Market risk, custody risk (mitigated)</span><span class="lang-zh">市場風險、託管風險（已緩解）</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/30">
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium">
              <span class="lang-en">ETH Staking (via VATP)</span><span class="lang-zh">ETH質押（經VATP）</span>
            </td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="text-green-400"><span class="lang-en">Regulated</span><span class="lang-zh">受監管</span></span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Slashing risk, lockup, market risk</span><span class="lang-zh">罰沒風險、鎖定期、市場風險</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/30">
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium">Polymarket</td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="text-yellow-400"><span class="lang-en">Unregulated</span><span class="lang-zh">未受監管</span></span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Smart contract, resolution, regulatory</span><span class="lang-zh">智能合約、結算、監管風險</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/30">
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium">Hyperliquid</td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="text-yellow-400"><span class="lang-en">Unregulated</span><span class="lang-zh">未受監管</span></span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Leverage, oracle, counterparty, regulatory</span><span class="lang-zh">槓桿、預言機、對手方、監管風險</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium">
              <span class="lang-en">AMM LP</span><span class="lang-zh">AMM流動性提供</span>
            </td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="text-yellow-400"><span class="lang-en">Unregulated</span><span class="lang-zh">未受監管</span></span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">IL, smart contract, rug pull, regulatory</span><span class="lang-zh">無常損失、智能合約、項目跑路、監管風險</span></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-green-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Need help with compliance assessment?</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">需要合規評估協助？</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">We can discuss how specific onchain products fit within the SFC framework for your firm.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">我們可以討論特定鏈上產品如何在SFC框架下適用於你的公司。</span>
        </p>
